headline: DAL Gains 31% in 6 Months: How Should Investors Play the Stock Now?

headline: United Airlines to Present at Barclays 43rd Annual Industrial Select Conference
summary: United will present at Barclays 43rd Annual Industrial Select Conference on Wednesday, February 18, beginning at 8:40 a.m. EST. On the webcast Mike Leskinen, Chief Financial Officer, will make remarks on current trends affecting our business.
